      "content": "The theft/mischief analogy isn't really helping us with the audit report though. We need concrete possibilities for the shrinkage. \n\nCould you expand on point 2? Are there specific \"unit of measure\" errors or \"logging lag\" scenarios that typically cause a variance of 1-3% like we're seeing here?",
